1
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:12,560
Ayun,

2
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:13,920
no!

3
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,640
Ayun.

4
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:32,320
Ayun.

5
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,000
My lord.

6
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,920
Jiuyun,

7
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,720
this is a phoenix hairpin I specially found for you.

8
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,980
Let me put it on for you.

9
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,000
You don't like it?

10
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:08,080
Then I'll change the style.

11
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:11,180
I will satisfy whatever you want.

12
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:13,120
I said it before.

13
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,720
I will make you the happiest woman in the world.

14
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,920
Don't waste your effort.

15
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,200
I don't care about this.

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,360
I just want to know how A'yu is doing.

17
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,080
He is just my shadow.

18
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,920
I gave him his life,

19
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,840
his face,

20
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,600
and his identity.

21
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,920
I created his existence to protect you.

22
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,560
Why don't you understand me?

23
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:49,120
I hope you keep your promise.

24
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:51,080
If anything happens to Yu,

25
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,009
I won't let you get away with it.

26
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,680
Do you like him that much?

27
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,480
Don't worry.

28
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,560
I won't touch him

29
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,400
as long as you stay by my side.

30
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,520
How did you become like this?

31
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,120
The Gu Chengyu I know isn't like this.

32
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,200
Then from now on,

33
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,960
I will let you get to know me again.

34
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,800
Jiuyun.

35
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,090
Jiuyun, what's wrong with you?

36
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,560
Doctor, how is she?

37
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:36,400
Minister, the Princess's pulse is sometimes extremely weak,

38
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,320
and sometimes incredibly fast.

39
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:40,000
This depletion of the five viscera,

40
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:43,120
I have only seen it in people in their seventies.

41
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:47,140
It must be a backlash from the elixir.

42
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,480
What should we do?

43
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,800
I can write a prescription

44
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,680
for the Princess to recuperate.

45
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,079
However, although the Princess's pulse doesn't indicate imminent death,

46
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,540
she has a fatal condition.

47
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,560
I'm afraid it's hard to save her.

48
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,800
Do you

49
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,880
want to get revenge on Su Cheng

50
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,560
and win back the woman you love?

51
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,960
Ayu.

52
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,079
Ayu.

53
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,200
Don't go.

54
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,120
In my daze last night,

55
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,520
I clearly saw Ayu.

56
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,440
Was I just dreaming?

57
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,040
Ayu.

58
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,720
Somebody!

59
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,200
Princess.

60
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,399
Where is Su Cheng?

61
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,459
Master is having a meeting next door.

62
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,040
Got it.

63
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,960
You may leave.

64
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:24,520
Yes.

65
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,880
He was heavily guarded, how could he escape?

66
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,720
Not only that.

67
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,840
We searched the whole city but couldn't find Mo Yu's whereabouts.

68
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,840
It's like he vanished into thin air.

69
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,760
I heard that last night,

70
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:46,680
enemy spies assassinated the Beidi Queen's entourage.

71
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,720
Yes.

72
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,520
Could it be that Mo Yu's disappearance

73
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,460
is related to the enemy spies?

74
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,800
Mo Yu knows too many secrets.

75
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,200
We can't let him fall into the spies' hands.

76
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:00,080
You mean...

77
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,200
Only dead men

78
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,480
tell no tales.

79
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:31,640
My Lord,

80
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,900
is it of any use for us to wait here?

81
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,520
I spread the word

82
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,200
that this place will be seized tomorrow.

83
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,200
They will definitely come tonight.

84
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,280
Something is moving.

85
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,600
Yu.

86
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,240
It's an ambush! Run!

87
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,480
I guessed you would follow me.

88
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,560
The man in black is a trick I arranged to lure you out.

89
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,760
Take her back to the Su Residence first.

90
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,120
Yu.

91
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:14,560
Yun.

92
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,400
You are still alive.

93
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,080
I'm fine.

94
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,860
Zhong Xiaqiang

95
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,520
Zijian Qiangqipin Pengyin

96
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,180
Quan Xuhang

97
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,200
Quan Yulong

98
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:41,860
Quan Yulong

99
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:42,760
Licheng Lefei

100
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,040
Luo Xiaocong Linxunbo
